➜FBI试图迫使Google解锁用户的Android手机
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=28728	27000
联邦调查局无法破译Android手机的屏幕解锁图案，<a href="http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/news/2012/03/fbi-stumped-by-pimps-androids-pattern-lock-serves-warrant-on-google.ars">它试图迫使搜索巨人帮它解锁</a>。<i>
